Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒問題  直擊您的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新卡諾奴瓦魯X
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午要接受採訪和綵排
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總是那麼可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您過獎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上去慣例的廣播節目和綵排
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自筆名為若木民喜先生的來信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你變臉變得太快了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直做嘉音很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  你還在鼓起勁努力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:48.73,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look up at the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:51.36,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Like a bird without wings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:53.76,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}If you want to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:57.12,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Feel your breeze, release yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.64,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.23,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count your blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:03.59,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Every time you try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:10.57,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Find something, believe yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:21.09,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}My mission is gonna be a tough one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:23.69,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I know it's not a game anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:26.75,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I swear that I'll never fail again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:29.97,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}'Cuz don't wanna regret anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.47,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you hear I'm calling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:35.18,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I just wanna feel you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:38.01,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't forget to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:40.73,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So please remember
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.69,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I hear you are calling me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:46.46,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I want you to feel me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:49.35,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You know I won't surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.16,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Never surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:54.96,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}My mission I've got to execute
